20:48.120 --> 20:51.578
So I see. Ten dollars, please.

20:57.830 --> 20:58.660
Thanks.

20:59.170 --> 21:00.580
[cash register whirring]

21:05.130 --> 21:09.248
Hey, if you want, we can go
grab coffee together afterwards.

21:10.140 --> 21:12.631
