21:15.140 --> 21:16.767
Jess, we're gonna miss the trailers.

21:17.980 --> 21:21.859
Go. Enjoy the movie. I--
You know, we can catch up whenever.

21:27.320 --> 21:29.527
Jesus,
you're always putting me on the spot.

21:29.620 --> 21:32.441
Fuck girl code.
Hannah's above all that shit.

21:32.540 --> 21:33.438
I guess.

21:35.000 --> 21:37.036
-She seemed cool, right?
-Yes!

21:37.750 --> 21:39.786
Can we just enjoy
