She's totally jealous, like, obsessed.

22:49.610 --> 22:51.316
-Shut up, really?
-Yeah.

22:52.410 --> 22:55.732
-What did she say?
-A lot. She's hurt.

22:58.080 --> 23:01.208
But, Jess, I don't want to break up
over someone else's drama.

23:01.290 --> 23:02.120
Neven

23:04.250 --> 23:09.256
But we should probably just, you know,
back off until she gets over it.

23:09.510 --> 23:10.795
-[audience member] Shh!
-Yeah.

23:12.340 --> 23:14.171
-Here.
-Thank you.

23:14.260 --> 23:17.138
[Jessica] From that point,
Alex and I kept things cool.

23:17.930 --> 23:22.640
But when Hannah found out that he made
that list, it was too much for her.

23:22.730 --> 23:27.599
So you blame the Hot or Not List,
and the culture at Liberty,

23:27.690 --> 23:30.067
_ but isn't it true
that It was Hannah's jealousy

23:30.150 --> 23:31.196
that ended your friendship?

23:31.820 --> 23:33.196
No. It was the list.

23:33.910 --> 23:36.731
After you broke up with Alex,
did your friendship with Hannah resume?

23:38.330 --> 23:39.866
-No.
-Because you started

23:39.960 --> 23:42.531
-dating Justin Foley, correct?
-No.

23:42.620 --> 23:44.030
So you didn't date Justin Foley?

23:44.330 --> 23:48.369
-No, I did--
-Hannah was jealous of you and Justin,

23:48.840 --> 23:51.081
just like she was jealous
of you and Alex, wasn't she?

23:51.170 --> 23:53.502
-No, that's not true.
-How do you know?

23:55.720 --> 23:58.211
-[Sonya] Jessica, how do you know?
-How do you know?

24:00.390 --> 24:04.895
Jessica, isn't it true that Hannah Baker
was jealous, and vindictive,

24:04.980 --> 24:06.936
-and that is why your friendship ended?
-No.

24:07.110 --> 24:10.238
Well, the prosecution claims
that it was the Hot or Not List,

24:10.570 --> 24:13.152
but it was simply Hannah's own jealousy,
isn't that correct?

24:16.120 --> 24:18.111
There's no other reason, is there?

24:19.580 --> 24:20.569
[Sonya] Jessica.

24:27.540 --> 24:31.089
Jessica? Is there any other reason
that we haven't mentioned?

24:34.930 --> 24:37.046
No. There's no other reason.

24:38.310 --> 24:39.129
[Sonya] I see.

24:41.060 --> 24:42.266
No further questions.

24:50.280 --> 24:53.101
-I gotta go.
-You're leaving? She's not done.

24:53.450 --> 24:54.644
[Clay] I heard enough.

24:57.280 --> 25:01.159
-Yeah, me, too. You coming?
-I'll leave when Jess is done.

25:01.410 --> 25:02.570
Did you really kiss Hannah?

25:03.960 --> 25:05.075
Yeah. It was a friend thing.

25:10.670 --> 25:12.877
[water running]

25:13.550 --> 25:14.926
[door opening]

25:19.430 --> 25:22.467
-I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
-It's okay.

25:22.560 --> 25:24.881
No, Hannah was my friend,
I just wanted to help her.

25:24.980 --> 25:26.186
You did, honey. You did.

25:26.270 --> 25:28.511
[cries]

25:30.320 --> 25:31.139
Jessica.

25:32.690 --> 25:34.180
