two friends of mine who are together,

41:03.290 --> 41:04.666
calling them faggots and shit.

41:05.420 --> 41:08.241
I got Lewis to bounce the skater kid
for being overage.

41:08.590 --> 41:13.459
We told Jacket he could stay,
but he was loyal and he took off.

41:14.130 --> 41:15.119
Haven't seen him since.

41:16.140 --> 41:20.588
Any idea where the kid skates? Or squats?

41:22.350 --> 41:24.136
[indistinct chattering]

41:29.690 --> 41:30.645
[Clay] Jesus.

41:32.990 --> 41:37.905
-People actually live here?
-Apparently. Come on.

41:40.080 --> 41:42.617
_Excuse me.
We're looking for a friend of ours.

41:42.700 --> 41:43.746
Have you seen this guy?

41:44.500 --> 41:45.319
[woman] No.

41:45.410 --> 41:47.071
-All right. Thank you.
-Sorry.

41:47.920 --> 41:50.662
_Excuse me.
We're looking for a friend of ours.

41:53.710 --> 41:56.679
Excuse me.
We're looking for a friend of mine.

41:57.090 --> 41:58.500
This guy. Have you seen him?

42:03.310 --> 42:06.382
Tony. We look like narcs.

42:07.060 --> 42:07.890
Okay.

42:08.270 --> 42:09.089
Can you help me?

42:13.570 --> 42:14.810
-Tony.
-What?

42:18.610 --> 42:20.771
-Can you spare some change?
-[Tony chuckles]

42:22.700 --> 42:25.908
Incentive. We need to offer incentive.
What do you have?

42:26.410 --> 42:28.162
[Tony] I fucking drove.
You don't have cash?

42:28.250 --> 42:31.993
No, I'll pay you back tomorrow,
with interest. Come on.

42:37.840 --> 42:38.795
[Clay] Uh...

42:40.390 --> 42:42.176
Have you ever seen this kid here before?

42:44.970 --> 42:45.800
Maybe.

42:47.890 --> 42:49.551
Will $10 help you remember?

42:50.730 --> 42:52.266
I think 20 would help me remember more.

42:59.910 --> 43:03.323
-There he is!
-Justin! Yo, Foley!

43:03.950 --> 43:05.156
Foley!

43:05.580 --> 43:07.616
-Hey! Where'd you get that jacket?
-What was that?

43:07.710 --> 43:09.575
You heard him, the jacket.
Where'd you get it?

43:09.870 --> 43:11.451
Goodwill. The fuck is it to you?

43:11.540 --> 43:14.168
-Don't fuck with me, man.
-Okay, Tiny.

43:14.960 --> 43:17.258
-[grunting]
'[guy] Whoa! Check it out!

43:19.630 --> 43:20.710
[clamoring]

43:21.680 --> 43:23.545
-Who the fuck do you think you are?
-Tony!

43:23.640 --> 43:25.881
Waste my time and I will fucking end you,
understand?

43:25.970 --> 43:27.267
-Tony, let go!
-Where is he?

43:27.350 --> 43:29.386
He was sparing change on BART
a couple weeks back.

43:29.730 --> 43:32.472
-When's the last time you saw him?
-Yesterday, in Chinatown.

43:34.650 --> 43:36.811
-[man] Damn!
-That's our friend that belongs to.

43:38.320 --> 43:40.311
-Tony, come on, let's go. Let's go.
-What the hell?

43:40.400 --> 43:41.776
-Where did that come from?
-Take the jacket.

43:51.170 --> 43:53.661
Wait. Wait, wait. I think that's him.

43:54.080 --> 43:56.742
-Jesus, that can't be him.
-Justin.

43:58.510 --> 44:00.000
Wait! Justin! God damn it!

44:01.300 --> 44:02.540
Fuck. Just--

44:05.050 --> 44:06.301
[Justin groans]

44:06.510 --> 44:07.636
You fucking kids!

44:08.770 --> 44:10.806
How many times do I have to tell you?

44:10.890 --> 44:14.348
Doing your drugs in my alley.
This is private property!

44:14.940 --> 44:16.567
I called the cops!

44:17.520 --> 44:19.568
Justin. Justin! Jessica wants you back.

44:20.320 --> 44:21.560
-Fuck you.
-No, she does.

44:21.650 --> 44:23.982
-I just talked to her yesterday.
-She hates me, okay?

44:24.070 --> 44:26.868
No, she doesn't.
She wants you to come back. [pants]

44:28.950 --> 44:30.247
[engine revs]

44:30.330 --> 44:31.536
[siren wails]

44:32.250 --> 44:35.242
I will leave both of you
if you don't get in my fucking car now!

44:35.790 --> 44:37.746
[siren blaring]

44:49.060 --> 44:50.630
[doorbell rings]

44:51.890 --> 44:53.187
[sighs]

44:56.060 --> 44:56.890
Good evening.

44:57.230 --> 45:01.064
Um, Mrs. Walker, I'm Kevin Porter
from Liberty High School.

45:02.070 --> 45:05.483
I know who you are.
I didn't realize you made house calls.

45:06.070 --> 45:07.947
I would like to talk to you
about your son,

45:08.280 --> 45:11.249
and his interaction with girls
at Liberty High School.

45:11.910 --> 45:13.070
My husband isn't home.

45:14.670 --> 45:15.489
Okay.

45:19.250 --> 45:20.080
Come in.

45:20.920 --> 45:23.969
-Can I get you something to drink?
-No, thank you.

45:25.220 --> 45:28.212
And I left a few messages at your house

45:28.300 --> 45:31.849
until your mom picked up
and told me to stop calling. So...

45:33.980 --> 45:36.016
Aanay, um...

45:37.310 --> 45:38.607
Look, I hope I find you.

45:40.360 --> 45:42.316
And I won't call you back again.

45:44.490 --> 45:48.403
I mean, I might call you back.
[stammers] I'll probably call you back.

45:49.870 --> 45:52.111
[sighs] Okay. Bye.

45:52.200 --> 45:54.953
In my experience,
a girl who doesn't call you back

45:55.080 --> 45:57.287
-is a girl who doesn't wanna talk to you.
-Rea|ly?

45:57.710 --> 45:59.587
You're gonna tell me
about your experience?

45:59.670 --> 46:02.958
Look, all I'm saying
is that Skye Miller is a piece of work.

46:03.050 --> 46:04.085
She's fucked up.

46:04.300 --> 46:05.119
She's--?

46:07.630 --> 46:10.542
I think you should stop talking,
like, for the foreseeable future.

46:11.560 --> 46:13.551
Good. You're alive.

46:15.270 --> 46:16.259
[Tony] Drink.

46:19.650 --> 46:21.936
-You're welcome.
-You'll feel much better after a meal.

46:22.360 --> 46:23.850
-And a shower.
-Fuck you.

46:26.400 --> 46:27.901
Your mom still live in the same place?

46:28.780 --> 46:32.272
-Shit, I can't go back there.
-What? Why?

46:33.580 --> 46:36.287
I took some money from her boyfriend
before I left.

46:36.500 --> 46:38.206
If he finds out I'm there, he'll kill me.

46:38.540 --> 46:39.916
So what the fuck do we do with him?

46:41.920 --> 46:44.297
[Jessica]
Friendship is a complicated thing...

46:47.800 --> 46:49.836
especially between girls.

46:50.300 --> 46:53.463
And it gets even more complicated
when there's a boy involved.

46:54.770 --> 46:56.089
But I can tell you one thing.

46:58.850 --> 47:01.057
Hannah's totally
Single White Female-ing you right now.

47:01.440 --> 47:04.011
I blame the boy more than I blame Hannah.

47:04.480 --> 47:06.027
Does that work if one of us is brown?

47:07.530 --> 47:10.192
-Just ignore her. That's what I do.
-[woman 1] Oh, shit.

47:11.320 --> 47:12.981
-Here she comes.
-Good luck with that.

47:13.700 --> 47:14.576
Bitches.

47:19.120 --> 47:20.781
-Hey.
-Hey.

47:22.500 --> 47:23.580
So...

47:25.380 --> 47:28.668
-You were pretty drunk the other night.
-Me and everyone else.

47:29.880 --> 47:33.543
