believe he would do that.

47:34.640 --> 47:37.302
Yeah, well,
maybe there's more to that story.

47:38.230 --> 47:39.049
What do you mean?

47:41.310 --> 47:42.436
Ijust...

47:44.230 --> 47:48.394
[sighs] Uh, listen, Jess, I, um...

47:50.450 --> 47:51.986
I saw something...

47:53.780 --> 47:56.829
-when you and Justin went into--
-Jesus, Hannah, seriously?

47:57.370 --> 48:01.079
First Alex and now Justin?
Look, I'm sorry, all right?

48:01.160 --> 48:03.958
I'm sorry that I'm making it work
with Justin and you couldn't.

48:04.380 --> 48:06.245
It's not my fault. Okay?

48:07.090 --> 48:09.797
-I'm--
-Jesus, some party.

48:12.720 --> 48:14.176
Yeah, some party.

48:14.470 --> 48:18.304
-It's so fucked up about Jeff.
-Yeah, it's all fucked up.

48:19.350 --> 48:22.387
-But, Jess and I had a good night, huh?
-Mm.

48:24.190 --> 48:27.182
-What are you--?
-Hannah, enough, all right?

48:27.270 --> 48:30.319
Can you just let me and Justin be happy?
Don't be a bitch.

48:31.150 --> 48:33.527
Yeah. Okay. Sorry.

48:35.910 --> 48:38.902
[Jessica] There are all different ways
boys mess with girls.

48:38.990 --> 48:44.201
And some of those ways,
well, we let them do it.

48:54.430 --> 48:55.749
[bottles clinking]

48:56.930 --> 48:58.056
[Lainie] Clay.

48:59.430 --> 49:02.809
There's something we'd like to talk
