49:04.060 --> 49:05.015
Coming.

49:06.940 --> 49:07.759
Shit.

49:13.700 --> 49:14.735
Clay, um...

49:16.110 --> 49:19.864
We, uh, recognize that, um...

49:20.040 --> 49:26.411
most kids, many kids your age
in our area have cars.

49:26.500 --> 49:28.741
Even though public transportation
is excellent in this county.

49:28.840 --> 49:34.210
We also recognize that riding
on county highways may be safer from...

49:35.130 --> 49:36.176
a car.

49:37.390 --> 49:41.508
No way. Wait, this is mine?
[stammers] That's...

49:42.850 --> 49:45.432
