I'm-- I'm hearing you.

50:02.080 --> 50:05.208
Though, it's even easier to sneak
around in a Prius. They're silent.

50:05.290 --> 50:09.374
No more sneaking around.
No more secrets. I promise.

50:11.800 --> 50:13.415
Make a sound, we're both dead.

50:16.010 --> 50:19.468
