to the detonator.

50:19.550 --> 50:22.053
-Yeah, just go-- Just like-- There we go.
-Oh, shit.

50:22.140 --> 50:23.846
-Is that supposed to happen?
-Yeah. Yeah.

50:23.930 --> 50:25.727
